## <a id='config-elb'></a>Step 22: Configure Router (or HAProxy) to Elastic Load Balancer ##

1. In the **Elastic Runtime** tile, click **Resource Config**.
  <%= image_tag("pcfaws/er-aws-resource-config.png") %>

